title: Gorgeous Corner Home With Queen Anne View and Rooftop Access!
posting_body: ['ICONIC QUEEN ANNE LIVING AT ROY & MERCER', 'Live next door to the Space Needle with direct connectivity to Seattle’s arts district at Center Steps.', 'In a vibrant new community establishing a gateway to Seattle Center from residential Uptown, you’ll find studio, one- and two-bedroom apartments with cutting-edge amenities and an unbeatably walkable Seattle location.', 'Call Now:', 'show contact info', 'x 19', 'OR Text', '19', 'to', 'show contact info', 'to text our team.', 'Interested in more information?', 'Visit link below:', '<URL>', 'This is a 1 Bedroom, 1 Bath, approximately 568-809 Sq.', 'Ft.', 'Features', '- Full size washer and dryer', '- Smart thermostats, select homes with Nest', '- Space Needle and city views*', '- Air conditioning *', '- Solid wood barn doors *', '- Vinyl plank flooring', '- Two unique color palettes with movable kitchen islands*', '- Custom Elfa closet system', '- Patio/balcony*', '*available in select homes', 'Community Amenities', '- Three unique rooftop decks that include fire pit, outdoor television, outdoor kitchens', '- Bike room with repair station', '- Two lounges – main floor and interior rooftop', '- Controlled access garage', '- 24 hour on-call maintenance', '- 24/7 state of the art fitness center – with integrated cardio theater/TVs', '- Recycling extra storage onsite available', '- EV parking stations', '- Controlled access community', '- Built green three star *', '- Through-block rain garden with sculpture displays by Miguel Edwards, Sarah Lavin, and Bocci', '- Pet friendly', '- Dog spa', '- Outdoor courtyard with ping pong table', '- On-site management', '- Rooftop pet park', '- Game room with pool, darts and sonos record player', '- Smart package room', '- Open co-work spaces', 'Center Steps', '225 Roy St., Seattle, WA, 98109']
